  "content": "\n\n<div id=\"comments\" class=\"comment-list new \">\n        <ul>\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1762842580\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"Porc au Prince\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/jeremydu777\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u3628707-30.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1762842580\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1762842580\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1762842580\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/jeremydu777\/\">Porc au Prince<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar40 rating\" title=\"推荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-24<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">电影不是外在的形式主义和象征，而是内在化的生命体验与时间的显现。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1762282855\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"执安\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/88212965\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com\/icon\/u88212965-9.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1762282855\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1762282855\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1762282855\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/88212965\/\">执安<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-23<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">20190417:5星\n对于普通人来说，电影可以是兴趣，也可以是乐趣。但是对于电影从业者来说，电影意味着什么？他们是为谁、又是为了什么而创作？现今成为一种全民娱乐活动的电影，其诞生时所具有的初衷和意义是否已面目全非？在本书中，塔可夫斯基还原了最初的电影世界，指出电影创作的实质，就是雕刻时光。\n对于老塔来说，电影是作为一门艺术独立存在的，电影固然受到绘画、文学、音乐等的滋养和影响，但是也同样需要脱离出来，实现其对时光中流淌的现象的观察。创作者需要深刻认识到生活的意义，并在工作过程中进行自我完善。艺术作品自有其使命，其命运则掌握在创作者手中，将世界的实质和真理反映给大众，将人的思想内心以及生命的意义完整的表达出来，让人们在观影过程中，感受到自己需要爱，感受到美好的召唤，这才应是电影创作者的责任。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1762071922\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"soloparati\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/Soloparati\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u3703805-11.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1762071922\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1762071922\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1762071922\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/Soloparati\/\">soloparati<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-23<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">诗性理想的极致。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1758666998\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"1900ocean\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/wlpfeiyang\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com\/icon\/u30973003-7.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1758666998\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1758666998\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1758666998\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/wlpfeiyang\/\">1900ocean<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-20<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">说的是电影 也是人生 怎么应对越来越强烈的个人的无力感 精神危机 塔可夫斯基强调个人的责任感 强大的内驱力 坚持自己对命运的主宰权 以道德和信仰 对抗物质生活  而对电影创作来说 任何虚假 做作的诗意都是不真诚的 导演必须真正掏心掏肺 他要是善感的 把现实的每一寸呼吸 时光的流淌 自然地展现给观众<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1757994495\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"旗木卡卡西\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/49412145\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com\/icon\/u49412145-16.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1757994495\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1757994495\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1757994495\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/49412145\/\">旗木卡卡西<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-19<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">看不懂老塔的电影？他自己写影评解释给你听，老塔着实是个彻头彻尾的艺术家啊！<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1756849245\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"十月曦瓦\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/153072909\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com\/icon\/u153072909-4.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1756849245\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1756849245\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1756849245\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/153072909\/\">十月曦瓦<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-18<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">读至情深落泪时！<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1756481930\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"JUNP\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/62696655\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com\/icon\/u62696655-6.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1756481930\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1756481930\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1756481930\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/62696655\/\">JUNP<\/a>\n                    <span>2019-04-22<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">不知道这是本什么书？评分竟然这么高 哪天去图书馆看看\n<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1755418610\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"向日葵先生\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/sunflower-yan\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com\/icon\/u1468487-7.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1755418610\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1755418610\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1755418610\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/sunflower-yan\/\">向日葵先生<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar40 rating\" title=\"推荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-12-14<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">书店半价，已入库，直觉文采好，找时间拜读。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1755294303\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"藠头与秋葵\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/1377398\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u1377398-3.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1755294303\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1755294303\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1755294303\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/1377398\/\">藠头与秋葵<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-05-09<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">真正的艺术家必须是真诚的，越是忠于自己才是忠于观众，而大师的诞生有赖于文化土壤和所处的时代，苏联文学对老塔的影响显著，老塔也坚信艺术创作从来都不是自由的（并不是说审查体系，而是哲学意义上的），非常有启发的一本书，无论是对于理解老塔的电影还是艺术美学。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1754431197\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"小螺号\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/151547492\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u151547492-1.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1754431197\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1754431197\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1754431197\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/151547492\/\">小螺号<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-16<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">读完之后，终于明白了当时看完《牺牲》走在路上时为什么会完全无法控制自己的情绪一边哭一边回家。塔可夫斯基的创作始终指向的是人类的本质，是对爱与永恒的追求，是为了维持人类最重要的信念而战斗，是通过艺术去支撑人最痛苦的希望。这和哈姆雷特的追问，生存还是毁灭，具有同样的意义。他对自己所有作品的认识还有思考，已然到达了哲学高度。他解答了我内心对电影创作的意义的困惑，也给我指明了通向大洋彼岸那座雾中灯塔的航路。那个若隐若现的召唤并不是我的错觉，那是一个明确的信号：为了一切永恒而牺牲自己有限的生命，灵魂才能安息。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1754160990\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"云雀叫了一整天\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/62839507\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u62839507-40.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1754160990\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1754160990\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1754160990\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/62839507\/\">云雀叫了一整天<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-05-08<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">诗学意义上的电影形象<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1753598127\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"福克钠\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/59290231\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u59290231-11.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1753598127\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1753598127\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1753598127\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/59290231\/\">福克钠<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-05-12<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">电影艺术启蒙<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1752993612\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"Coyotells\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/39254350\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u39254350-12.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1752993612\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1752993612\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1752993612\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/39254350\/\">Coyotells<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-14<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">精准<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1752185285\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"高山白早\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/83387941\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u83387941-11.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1752185285\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1752185285\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1752185285\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/83387941\/\">高山白早<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-08-09<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">最后一篇说拍《牺牲》里面房子着火的第一回因为摄影机坏只能眼睁睁的看着布景被烧完，第二次拍的时候摄影师的手一直在抖，终于停机和老塔抱头痛哭。啊，老塔好的没边了，作为艺术家在于牺牲，作为导演在于雕刻时光。人的本性，对永恒不灭的，对爱的，对自由的追求都在于牺牲，在于用直面灵魂的折磨永不远离生活世界的对抗，幸福从来不是人的本性。电影不是符号语言，不需要模仿文字的表意方式，同样用俳句一比电影，爱森斯坦看到意境试图通过用影像模仿文学形式来展现，老塔意图直接用电影展现意境本身。时空里的意境本身不需要象征的介质，电影不需要编码和象征，电影直接让我们看见。老塔在文字上也极尽了坦诚，从稀薄空气和浓绿草地间泥泞的小路上骑自行车到达读者，在雾渐渐升起时讲话。爱老塔。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1751002171\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"绿桔\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/175072982\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u175072982-10.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1751002171\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1751002171\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1751002171\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/175072982\/\">绿桔<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-09-22<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">关于电影，他认为艺术是给人直接的美感，不需要加以太多的象征意义！\n关于世界，他认为每个人都应该对自己有所思考，不要被物质所投喂！\n关于自己，他学习诗人，作家，同行的精神，却也敢于批判，思辨且不断自省！\n<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1748430332\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"苏影\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/164277414\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img1.doubanio.com\/icon\/u164277414-8.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1748430332\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1748430332\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1748430332\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/164277414\/\">苏影<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-09-27<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">他是特立独行的导演，思维缜密的哲学家，平易近人的朋友。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1748308319\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"May\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/annatom\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u51344069-13.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1748308319\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1748308319\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1748308319\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/annatom\/\">May<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-10<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">获益匪浅，一本蕴藏智慧又没什么废话的好书啊<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1748226075\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"萘烃锆\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/194770718\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com\/icon\/u194770718-5.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1748226075\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1748226075\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1748226075\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/194770718\/\">萘烃锆<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar40 rating\" title=\"推荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-04-10<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">电影观艺术观，松散的思想随笔，但理论苍白，艺术常青，塔可夫斯基是艺术家，读这随笔集绝不如去钻研他的作品。文句不好读但文意绝对严谨，感到是俄罗斯民族的文学特征。210至214页对索拉里斯、镜子和潜行者的阐释很有意义。最重要的是电影形象和电影真实，日本俳句的影响，拒绝隐喻。陀思妥耶夫斯基群魔，普希金的诗先知。<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1746888907\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"不系舟\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/77082644\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img9.doubanio.com\/icon\/u77082644-26.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1746888907\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1746888907\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1746888907\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n                    <a href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/77082644\/\">不系舟<\/a>\n                        <span class=\"user-stars allstar50 rating\" title=\"力荐\"><\/span>\n                    <span>2019-06-21<\/span>\n                <\/span>\n            <\/h3>\n            <p class=\"comment-content\">\n            \n                <span class=\"short\">没看过电影就来看书读者不是一个好观众<\/span>\n            <\/p>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/li>\n\n                \n    <li class=\"comment-item\" data-cid=\"1745144264\">\n            <div class=\"avatar\">\n                <a title=\"如是我闻_一时\" href=\"https:\/\/www.douban.com\/people\/158495497\/\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img3.doubanio.com\/icon\/u158495497-22.jpg\">\n                <\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">\n            <h3>\n                <span class=\"comment-vote\">\n                    <span id=\"c-1745144264\" class=\"vote-count\">0<\/span>\n                        <a href=\"javascript:;\" id=\"btn-1745144264\" class=\"j a_show_login\" data-cid=\"1745144264\">有用<\/a>\n                <\/span>\n                <span class=\"comment-info\">\n       